death.attack.asyetuntitled.charlie: %1$s was killed by something in the darkness...
asyetuntitled.darkness.enter.message8: Darkness approaches from outside. I feel no light inside me strong enough to resist it.
asyetuntitled.darkness.enter.message10: Night will fall and the dark will rise when a good man goes to war.
asyetuntitled.darkness.enter.message11: Not everyone comes back out of the dark.
asyetuntitled.darkness.enter.message12: Lost in the darkness... Silence surrounds me...
asyetuntitled.charlie.scare.message1: I don't think I'm alone out here...
asyetuntitled.charlie.scare.message13: I was merely adopted by the dark; this monster was born in it...
asyetuntitled.charlie.scare.message14: There are things waiting in the darkness. Creatures of metal, fire, and blood.
asyetuntitled.charlie.scare.message15: It's what's in the dark. It's Vashta Nerada!
asyetuntitled.charlie.attack.message4: The Prince of Darkness is supposed to be a gentleman!
asyetuntitled.darkness.gone.message7: It is better to light a candle than to curse the darkness.
asyetuntitled.darkness.gone.message8: All the darkness in the world cannot extinguish the light of a single candle.
asyetuntitled.darkness.gone.message9: At the darkest moment comes the light.
asyetuntitled.darkness.gone.message10: I'd rather stay in the light!
